Reviews

review by - Yelp

Hosea B:

I truly wish I could explain how good this food is. I'm from Charleston so I know good red rice. Growing up here I also know good seafood. THIS PLACE IS KILL'N IT!!!! And God forbid I tell you about the dessert!!!

review by - Yelp

Daniel G:

PHENOMENAL! SERVICE WAS AMAZING and FOOD WAS TO DIE FOR. Brisket fries, fried chicken and patty melt.. I would highly recommend anyone to come here.

review by - Yelp

David Q:

Great fried chicken. Family friendly spot and kids eat free. This is a great deal in Joe Biden's America where we have to watch our pennies. In all seriousness the food is great, servers are so nice and they have movies playing everywhere. Great music selection.

review by - Yelp

La'Maurice S:

Best food we've had in a long time! Everything was delicious! Really glad we decided to choose this restaurant! Highly recommended! Outstanding customer service !

review by - Yelp

Ken K:

Great meal and service! I loved my burger melt and red wine! The menu options were excellent! I look forward to my next visit. The staff was friendly and professional!

Ms. Rose's Fine Food and Cocktails

About us

At Ms. Rose’s, our mission is to be the favorite place to eat and drink in West Ashley and the surrounding Charleston area. We accomplish this through great food and drink, dependable friendly service and a fun, family-friendly environment.

Our top priority is to assure safe service and provide our customers with a comfortable space to dine while complying with the CDC guidelines for face masks and social distancing. We ask for your continued patience and kindness as we operate our establishment appropriately to suit these times.

Stay safe, be good to each other, wash your hands, wear your mask, and we look forward to seeing you again soon!

-Your Ms. Rose’s Family
